{"tid":565082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主，獨裁，個重點係掌權既人，必需要叻仔","createTime":"2018-02-18T16:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T16:29:42.000Z","uid":123335,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5b45e06e24cddc7bcae652b751dbf35cee2c4543","tid":565082,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:00:45.000Z","msg":"民主，掌權既人，係所有人民<br />\n若果民智開左，絕大多數人民都係叻仔，係高質<br />\n民主係一件好事 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n獨裁，掌權既人，係君主<br />\n權力集中係一人之上<br />\n若呢個人，係叻仔，係明君<br />\n獨裁係一件好事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以，盲目加入建制 / 加入民主派別<br />\n都係on99 <br />\n<br />\n根本建制冇話絕對好<br />\n民主都冇絕對好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好唔好<br />\n最後都係睇運"},{"pid":"a3c9aeb1ac12c672e440c6d1534f1459900c23cf","tid":565082,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:03:52.000Z","msg":"明君，昏君邊個知？<br />\n點解要買大細？"},{"pid":"dbd2f048727f20ba1b02f329a2401539ad367f95","tid":565082,"uid":140769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:05:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe9e3a45d7060abba0b2ac578d1657e6fb3764c8","tid":565082,"uid":142029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:05:24.000Z","msg":"叻仔會被推上當權 獨裁制度一耐 掌權人都會被權力腐化 享受特權 然後人民又會抗爭 <br />\n與其話係運 不如話係循環"},{"pid":"2e6b84ba6052192800d1a99c7a338f5f9cc49698","tid":565082,"uid":7837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:05:43.000Z","msg":"點為之好事？"},{"pid":"8035aecfd294c7323296cd04ef37489c825eb249","tid":565082,"uid":162424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:06:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6198a0258ac3587bf364d6e9a36d1ed2556bf0e","tid":565082,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:09:21.000Z","msg":"頭兩段同第三段結論無關<br />\n不論'盲目'信或做咩行為都係錯<br />\n<br />\n第三段又同第四段無關<br />\n第四段話咩都係運又係戇鳩"},{"pid":"6fd0d407c7eb05582846e9892bb4904eb704964d","tid":565082,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:14:40.000Z","msg":"頭兩段係話某些特定條件下民主或獨裁都可以係好事<br />\n但冇考慮哩啲條件出現既機會<br />\n<br />\n嗰謬誤等於，殺人某些情況下手係合理<br />\n不等於我'一般情況下'反對殺人係戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n如果以香港情況計，港豬係戇鳩鳩<br />\n但獨裁既政團係叫中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好學JR,乜春都加盲目兩個字，然後顛倒黑白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a9510a1684ea21a64a7f3ab204a988bce762c0","tid":565082,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbd2f048727f20ba1b02f329a2401539ad367f95","tid":565082,"uid":140769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:05:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:21:12.000Z","msg":"你舉d例子黎<br />\n咩叫獨好多時好過民主tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ef0612a1eff1a03da578c7f4aab9fa5955dc6e","tid":565082,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59a9510a1684ea21a64a7f3ab204a988bce762c0","tid":565082,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbd2f048727f20ba1b02f329a2401539ad367f95","tid":565082,"uid":140769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:05:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:21:12.000Z","msg":"你舉d例子黎<br />\n咩叫獨好多時好過民主tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:22:49.000Z","msg":"舊時：<br />\n英政府<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時：<br />\n新加坡"},{"pid":"7172ffe0f9f7d7358600f446a94cfa6ba72a284e","tid":565082,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98ef0612a1eff1a03da578c7f4aab9fa5955dc6e","tid":565082,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59a9510a1684ea21a64a7f3ab204a988bce762c0","tid":565082,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbd2f048727f20ba1b02f329a2401539ad367f95","tid":565082,"uid":140769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:05:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:21:12.000Z","msg":"你舉d例子黎<br />\n咩叫獨好多時好過民主tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:22:49.000Z","msg":"舊時：<br />\n英政府<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時：<br />\n新加坡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:24:12.000Z","msg":"好多時？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502f4b45b4d50c59fff00e0045c641d2264ba013","tid":565082,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:27:46.000Z","msg":"依家香港個建制 支<br />\n就一定唔係咩好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40eac471f50232e95fe06895d89cfb30f8f7ab5","tid":565082,"uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6fd0d407c7eb05582846e9892bb4904eb704964d","tid":565082,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:14:40.000Z","msg":"頭兩段係話某些特定條件下民主或獨裁都可以係好事<br />\n但冇考慮哩啲條件出現既機會<br />\n<br />\n嗰謬誤等於，殺人某些情況下手係合理<br />\n不等於我'一般情況下'反對殺人係戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n如果以香港情況計，港豬係戇鳩鳩<br />\n但獨裁既政團係叫中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好學JR,乜春都加盲目兩個字，然後顛倒黑白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:28:54.000Z","msg":"但以香港黎計<br />\n發展民主係好過俾中共管既<br />\n始終廢老都離死期不遠 <br />\n<br />\n所以依家發展定民主就差唔多啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但點解我話民主未必好？<br />\n你睇下印度 <br />\n印度正正就係一個印度既國家<br />\nd 國民根本未成氣候，俾d 豬隊友治國真係冚國剷"},{"pid":"ac8c8418e463f6ab1cf4aaefe91f20ae254ab653","tid":565082,"uid":140769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:29:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c27c3e9279a5ab66a4838e5500be5bf219277d1","tid":565082,"uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:29:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>頭兩段係話某些特定條件下民主或獨裁都可以係好事<br />\n但冇考慮哩啲條件出現既機會<br />\n<br />\n嗰謬誤等於，殺人某些情況下手係合理<br />\n不等於我'一般情況下'反對殺人係戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n如果以香港情況計，港豬係戇鳩鳩<br />\n但獨裁既政團係叫中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好學JR,乜春都加盲目兩個字，然後顛倒黑白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>但以香港黎計<br />\n發展民主係好過俾中共管既<br />\n始終廢老都離死期不遠 <br />\n<br />\n所以依家發展定民主就差唔多啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但點解我話民主未必好？<br />\n你睇下印度 <br />\n印度正正就係一個<span style=\"color: red;\">民主</span>既國家<br />\nd 國民根本未成氣候，俾d 豬隊友治國真係冚國剷</blockquote>"}]}